---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { CONTACT_EMAIL } from '../../lib/constants';
---
<BaseLayout title="Privacy" description="Privacy policy.">
  <article class="py-5 md:py-8">
    <h1 class="font-display text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight md:text-4xl">Privacy</h1>

    <div class="prose mt-4">
      <p>
        Controller: Michael Linder, Nötsch im Gailtal, Austria.<br />
        Contact: <a href={`mailto:${CONTACT_EMAIL}`}>{CONTACT_EMAIL}</a>
      </p>

      <h2>What this site does not do</h2>
      <p>
        No tracking. No cookies. No analytics. No data shared with third parties. The only client-side storage is your light/dark preference in localStorage.
      </p>

      <h2>Hosting</h2>
      <p>
        This site is hosted on private infrastructure and served via Cloudflare Tunnel. Cloudflare processes connection data (IP, timestamp, URL) to ensure availability. Legal basis: Art. 6(1)(f) GDPR. Cloudflare is certified under the EU-U.S. Data Privacy Framework.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        If you email me, your data is stored to handle the enquiry. No disclosure to third parties. Legal basis: Art. 6(1)(f) GDPR.
      </p>

      <h2>Your rights</h2>
      <p>
        Access, rectification, erasure, restriction, portability, objection. Complaints to the <a href="https://www.dsb.gv.at" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Austrian Data Protection Authority</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
